## üèó AI Engineering & Infrastructure

### **AI Engineering ‚Äî Chip Huyen**  
Industry guide to production ML systems. Covers:  
- model deployment  
- monitoring & drift detection  
- real-time inference  
- data pipelines  
- lifecycle management  
- reliability engineering

### **Fundamentals of Data Engineering**  
Foundational text covering ingestion, storage, modeling, transformation, orchestration, and serving‚Äîcore infrastructure for real-world AI.

### **Algorithms for AI**  
Survey of classical and modern algorithms:  
search, heuristics, optimization, gradient descent, neural models, and reinforcement learning.

### **AI Student Handbook**  
Broad foundational material on ML, math, ethics, and research pathways for AI learners.

